These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: mauve, apricot
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, social-worker
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, baccarat
2 different games are played: bridge, canasta
1. the person who likes mauve is on the far right##1
2. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
3. the designer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Color       | apricot       | mauve |
| Job         | social-worker | designer  |
| Cigar       | baccarat    | vegafina    |
| Game   | canasta       | bridge      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, swisher
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, hip-hop
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, time-travel
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daffodil, marigold
1. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
2. the fan of ambient is on the far left##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Cigar      | swisher     | davidoff |
| Music-Genre           | ambient | hip-hop      |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel  | action      |
| Flower         | daffodil | marigold     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
2 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, ferret
City: hamburg, london
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: february, march
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, taxi
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person driving the taxi##1
3. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Pet      | guinea-pig | ferret  |
| City          | hamburg    | london   |
| Birthday   | march  | february   |
| Transport     | taxi     | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, photography
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, tiparillo
There are 2 different favourite colors: azure, yellow
1. the person who likes azure is on the far left##1
2. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea       | soy-milk |
| Hobby          | photography         | dancing    |
| Cigar           | tiparillo | swisher    |
| Color   | azure           | yellow   |

