.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skiing, swimming
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, february
2 different pets are kept: mouse, rabbit
There are 2 different nationalities: spanish, turkish
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the turkish##1
3. the owner of the mouse is the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Sport           | swimming | skiing     |
| Birthday   | april          | february |
| Pet           | mouse          | rabbit    |
| Nationality     | turkish            | spanish       |

 